®∏√]<?php exit; ?>a:1:{s:7:"content";a:158:{i:0;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1396";s:4:"name";s:11:"Access Bars";s:4:"slug";s:11:"access-bars";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1396";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:508:"Access Bars are 32 points on one‚Äôs head which when gently touched, release anything that doesn‚Äôt allow one to receive. These points have the storage of all the thoughts, beliefs, ideas, and emotions that one has stored in any lifetime. Each Access Bar session is capable of releasing 5-10 thousand years of limitations corresponding with the specific bar being touched. This is a nurturing and relaxing process where one can let go of any barriers and be willing to change in all aspects of one‚Äôs life.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"70";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"70";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1529";s:4:"name";s:5:"Acmos";s:4:"slug";s:5:"acmos";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1529";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:489:"Acmos Method is a special therapy for balancing the patient‚Äôs energy fields using a combination of traditional Chinese wisdom and scientific discoveries made in the field of modern molecular biology. The most important tool of Acmos Method is Acmos Lecher Antenna. It strengthens the body energetically and helps to cope with aggression, corrects the disturbances in the body‚Äôs energy field before they develop into illnesses and identifies deep physical or emotional energy blockages.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1527";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"4";}i:2;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1466";s:4:"name";s:11:"Acupressure";s:4:"slug";s:11:"acupressure";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1466";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:444:"Acupressure is an ancient healing therapy that uses the finger to apply gentle to firm pressure on key healing points that correspond with energy meridians throughout the body. This helps stimulate the body‚Äôs natural life force and self-healing abilities. This therapy releases muscular tension and is also effective in stress-related ailments. It increases circulation, reduces pain, enhances vibrancy of health and boosts the immune system.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:2:"61";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"50";}i:3;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1467";s:4:"name";s:11:"Acupuncture";s:4:"slug";s:11:"acupuncture";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1467";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:412:"Acupuncture comes from an ancient Chinese form of Energy Therapy that works by inserting very thin needles into the patient‚Äôs skin at specific points on the body. This practice corresponds to the nervous system and stimulates the flow of Chi at various depths, and gives benefits such as release of pain management, tension and energetic blocks and also aiding the body in healing itself from chronic ailments.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:2:"34";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"26";}i:4;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1554";s:4:"name";s:39:"Affirmation &amp; Visualization Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:33:"affirmation-visualization-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1554";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:428:"Affirmations are amazing tools for taking charge of co-creating our reality and moving beyond our self-limiting beliefs. Affirmations are highly effective in manifesting opportunities and pursuing one‚Äôs desires since they are framed in the present tense, positive and rooted in the power of intention. A guided visual journey,using the power of the mind which is coupled with imagination, is a very effective tool for healing.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"17";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"14";}i:5;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1437";s:4:"name";s:15:"Akashic Records";s:4:"slug";s:15:"akashic-records";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1437";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:646:"Akashic Records is an astral library. It acts as a central storehouse for every thought, word, emotion, intent and event felt by every soul since the beginning of Time. The knowledge, in subtle form, exists fluidly between the different realms of time (past, present and possible future) and can be accessed by an Akashic Records Reader through a deep meditative state. The Reader is trained to recognize and draw out the right information based on the seeker‚Äôs query. The collective wisdom of the Akashic Records can be tapped into to know one‚Äôs soul-purpose and to heal karmic patterns, dis-ease in the body or any mental or emotional pain.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:2:"11";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"11";}i:6;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1492";s:4:"name";s:24:"Ana Pana Sati Meditation";s:4:"slug";s:24:"ana-pana-sati-meditation";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1492";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:316:"Ana Pana Sati Meditation is a simple breath meditation in which the doer is only asked to observe the natural breath and become one with it. Ana-Pana means inhalation and exhalation, and Sati is Mindfulness. Healing and enlightenment can be achieved through this meditation, along with finding pleasure in stillness.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1491";s:5:"count";s:2:"40";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"8";}i:7;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1420";s:4:"name";s:13:"Angel Reading";s:4:"slug";s:13:"angel-reading";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1420";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:285:"Angel Reading is a non-denominational spiritual healing method that involves working with a person‚Äôs guardian angels and archangels to heal and harmonize every aspect of their life. Angel therapy also helps one to receive the divine guidance more clearly from the Creator and angels.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:2:"53";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"49";}i:8;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1501";s:4:"name";s:16:"Angelic Chanting";s:4:"slug";s:16:"angelic-chanting";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1501";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:501:"Angelic Chanting is a way of invoking a Higher Power like the angels and archangels for assistance, guidance, support or simply blessings. Everybody‚Äôs angels try to communicate with them through many ways. Many spiritual masters can also channel and communicate with angels, receive their messages and also teach others to directly communicate with them. Angelic chanting is a mantra, a sound-based incantation that invokes their energy and opens the heart chakra by radiating love &amp; compassion.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1499";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:9;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1435";s:4:"name";s:20:"Animal Communication";s:4:"slug";s:20:"animal-communication";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1435";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:651:"Animal Communication is a telepathic communication, facilitated by the Therapist, between the pet and its owner. The communication can happen with the pet that has passed, to help their owner cope with their grief and/or guilt. In living pets, this therapy helps to heal and remove energetic blocks that are causing an illness. This method also helps to soothe the animal through discomforting situations such as relocations, behavioural problems and in dire circumstances, to know if the animal wants to be euthanized due to terminal illness or grave injury. Animal communication involves the use of the pet‚Äôs photograph for the telepathic healing.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"6";}i:10;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1402";s:4:"name";s:19:"Applied Kinesiology";s:4:"slug";s:19:"applied-kinesiology";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1402";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:608:"Applied Kinesiology is also the study of biomechanics (body movement), and is also now known as a method of ‚Äòmuscle strength testing‚Äô. Applied Kinesiology is based on the belief that muscles are linked to specific organs and glands, and their weakness indicates problems such as nerve damage, low blood supply, chemical imbalance and other neurological issues. Practitioners diagnose and treat this by correcting the muscle weakness that corresponds to the internal organs. Treatments can range from testing and counseling coupled with deep massage, joint manipulation, acupuncture and dietary therapies.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"2";}i:11;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1468";s:4:"name";s:13:"Aroma Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:13:"aroma-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1468";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:485:"Aromatherapy uses natural fragrant oils extracted from herbs, flowers, fruits, barks, stems, leaves, roots and other parts of a plant to enhance psychological, spiritual and physical well-being. The inhaled aroma from these ‚Äúessential‚Äù oils is widely believed to stimulate brain functions, relax the neurological synapses as well as tap into memory. Essential oils can also be absorbed through the skin from where they travel through the bloodstream and promote whole-body healing.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1457";s:5:"count";s:2:"13";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"10";}i:12;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1848";s:4:"name";s:11:"Art Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:12:"arts-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1848";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:677:"Art Therapy uses creative method of expression as a form of therapy. A trained therapist can help the patient release deep-seated, suppressed trauma and negative emotions in the most positive, constructive way. It involves the use of creative techniques such as drawing, painting, collage, coloring, or sculpting. It can provide solutions to emotional issues without the use of words. Age and lack of art knowledge or skill are no obstacle for being healed through Art Therapy. 

Addictions, self-esteem issues, stress-related illnesses such as anxiety and depression, and coping with disabilities are some of the situations that can be successfully treated with Art Therapy.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1438";s:5:"count";s:2:"15";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"14";}i:13;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1438";s:4:"name";s:12:"Arts Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:11:"art-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1438";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:316:"Arts Therapy is a group of creative, art-based activities ranging from painting to dancing that can help overcome trauma and mental illnesses under the guidance of trained practitioners. Sometimes when the soul is too burdened to speak, it can express itself through art, sparking intense transformation and healing.";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:14;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1413";s:4:"name";s:13:"Ashtanga Yoga";s:4:"slug";s:13:"ashtanga-yoga";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1413";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:369:"Ashtanga Yoga as described by Patanjali in the Yoga sutras is the ‚Äúeight-limbs of Yoga‚Äù. This consists of practices that include internal and external purification processes, such as Yamas, Niyama, Asana, Pranayama, Pratyahara, Dharana, Dhyana and Samadhi. This is an all-inclusive way of life as the cleansing is believed to bring one closer to the Universal Self.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1410";s:5:"count";s:3:"135";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:3:"115";}i:15;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1425";s:4:"name";s:12:"Aura Reading";s:4:"slug";s:12:"aura-reading";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1425";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:519:"Auras are colorful electromagnetic energy fields that contain information about the energy flow of people, animals and plants at a deeper level. Every aura has many layers including information about your life, connections, changing moods, to deep-set emotions, physical ailments and the areas where the energy flow is obstructed by trapped emotions within the body. An Aura reading can reveal temporary findings that show up as short-term problems and chronic ailments. One can also see the deeper makings of the soul.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:1:"8";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"8";}i:16;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"3622";s:4:"name";s:15:"Auriculotherapy";s:4:"slug";s:16:"auriculo-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"3622";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:481:"
This therapy can be likened to performing acupressure on the ear and traces back its roots to traditional Chinese medicine. It involves activating points on the skin of the outer ear or ‚Äòauricle‚Äô for healing as the ear is considered to be a micro-map of the entire body, representing all body parts. Consequently, any body ailment can be healed by means of the external ear. It is highly effective in treating pain, addictions, internal disorders and emotional issues. 


";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"5";}i:17;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1446";s:4:"name";s:12:"Auto Writing";s:4:"slug";s:12:"auto-writing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1446";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:347:"Auto Writing is a form of therapy where a steady stream of subconscious emotions, thoughts and expressions are released through automatic writing. One of the primary goals of auto-writing is to achieve a state of ‚Äúawareness‚Äù through a process of connecting with the source or simply unearthing repressed psychodynamic conflicts for resolution.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1438";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"4";}i:18;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1459";s:4:"name";s:8:"Ayurveda";s:4:"slug";s:8:"ayurveda";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1459";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:555:"Ayurveda is the science of life and was developed thousands of years ago. It was believed that the Gods passed down this knowledge to humans. One of the main principles of Ayurveda is that the body and mind are inextricably connected and that when the mind is brought into balance, it has immense healing power as that balance extends to the body. It is a method of healing the body from illnesses by using a combination of treatments that include detoxification, cleansing, massage, dietary control, herbal medicines, communion with nature, and exercise.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1457";s:5:"count";s:2:"76";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"35";}i:19;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1461";s:4:"name";s:20:"Bach Flower Remedies";s:4:"slug";s:20:"bach-flower-remedies";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1461";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:420:"Bach Flower Remedies uses 38 different flower essences distilled in water with the help of sun exposure or boiling. A special tincture is developed using these flowers which when taken orally can restore the internal balance and harmony between the mind, body and soul. This facilitates the natural healing abilities of the body to transform negative emotions while bringing about a sense of happiness and peace of mind.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1457";s:5:"count";s:2:"38";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"37";}i:20;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1539";s:4:"name";s:19:"Behavioural Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:19:"behavioural-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1539";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:206:"Behavioral therapy seeks to identify and help change potentially self-destructive or unhealthy behaviors. It functions on the idea that all behaviors are learned and that unhealthy behaviors can be changed.";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:21;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1506";s:4:"name";s:15:"BIOFIELD READER";s:4:"slug";s:15:"biofield-reader";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1506";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:511:"Biofield Reader uses photographic filters to read auras. There are many layers to an aura: the outer layers indicate moods, emotions and thoughts and can change from moment to moment whereas the deeper layers of the aura do not change momentarily and indicate most deeply ingrained emotional and energetic issues. It filters gradations and light that cannot be seen by the naked eye, gives information on a person‚Äôs general energy levels and any imbalances and blocks, along with offering Live Aura Streaming.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1503";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:22;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1475";s:4:"name";s:9:"Body work";s:4:"slug";s:9:"body-work";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1475";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:97:"Breathwork includes a variety of body manipulation therapies used for relaxation and pain relief.";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:1:"8";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"3";}i:23;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1478";s:4:"name";s:13:"Bowen Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:13:"bowen-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1478";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:541:"Bowen Therapy is a dynamic system of muscle and connective tissue therapy. It utilizes subtle inputs to the body known as moves, stimulating the body to heal itself, often profoundly. The practitioner‚Äôs moves deliver signals to the nervous system at specific locations (on muscles, tendons, ligaments, or nerves), and the body responds in its own time, within its vital capacity. It provides relief for many types of injuries and health problems, both acute and chronic, and is appropriate for people of all ages, in all degrees of health.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"4";}i:24;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1535";s:4:"name";s:10:"Breathwork";s:4:"slug";s:10:"breathwork";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1535";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:231:"These are unique and powerful conscious breathing techniques that aid in releasing the birth trauma and other limiting traumas encoded in all levels of our cells. Breathwork helps release physical and emotional toxins from the root";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:2:"10";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"4";}i:25;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1432";s:4:"name";s:13:"Candle Magick";s:4:"slug";s:13:"candle-magick";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1432";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:566:"Candle Magick is the manifestation of one‚Äôs deepest desires by tapping into the element of fire. Fire has the ability to exist in the physical realm as well as carry, release and move energy into the subtler etheric realms. In combination with some mantras, fire can tend to be the strongest of all elements in manifesting intentions, completing karmas and releasing energy into the realms beyond. Candle Magick can be used to improve any areas of one‚Äôs life: personal growth, professional struggles, relationships and old karma or letting go of energy patterns.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"4";}i:26;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1436";s:4:"name";s:10:"Cartomancy";s:4:"slug";s:10:"cartomancy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1436";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:566:"Cartomancy is a form of fortune-telling and the reading is done using a deck of cards. Though Tarot Cards were more popular, from 18th to 20th century playing cards were also used. These cards probably originated in China but gypsy travellers were the ones who spread this method of divination across Europe from 14th century onwards. A standard deck might contain a couple of jokers and even a blank card in addition to the 52-card, four-suit set. Each of these cards signifies a particular meaning and the Reader interprets them based on the order they are chosen.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:27;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1429";s:4:"name";s:10:"Channeling";s:4:"slug";s:10:"channeling";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1429";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:377:"Channeling is the process of communicating with any being that is not in human form by allowing that consciousness to express itself through an individual, the channel. It is a method used to access information, guidance and blessings from entities that are more evolved and could therefore enlighten us as we move through the evolution of consciousness and back to the source.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:2:"11";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"10";}i:28;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1499";s:4:"name";s:8:"Chanting";s:4:"slug";s:8:"chanting";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1499";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1491";s:5:"count";s:2:"13";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"6";}i:29;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1558";s:4:"name";s:23:"Children‚Äôs Counseling";s:4:"slug";s:19:"childrens-counselor";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1558";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:208:"It helps to release bad memories, cope with negative feeling, gain control on your action and thoughts, recognize your inner strength, reduce stress levels and increase the level of happiness one experiences.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1557";s:5:"count";s:2:"17";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"14";}i:30;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1464";s:4:"name";s:26:"Chinese / Tibetan Medicine";s:4:"slug";s:24:"chinese-tibetan-medicine";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1464";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:716:"Chinese/ Tibetan Medicine -Tibetan medicine combines principles of Ayurveda and the natural bounty of the Himalayas with the philosophical and spiritual beliefs of the Buddhist faith.It is based on 5 elements: Earth, Water,Fire, Air and Space. The treatment includes medicines composed of natural minerals and herbs as well as physical therapies such as Tibetan acupuncture and moxibustion. It helps to cure nervous issue,digestive disorders, heartburn, back pain, asthma, arthritis, eczema, sinusitis, liver problems/disorders, kidney problems/disorders, circulation issues, anxiety, sleep disorders, high blood pressure, stress and tension, allergic skin reactions, sexual dysfunction, overall health and vitality.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1457";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:31;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1540";s:4:"name";s:29:"Cognitive Behavioural Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:29:"cognitive-behavioural-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1540";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:581:"Cognitive Behavioural Therapy (CBT) is a form of counseling that can help us manage our problems by becoming consciously aware of our patterns and what causes them, thereby changing the way we think and behave. CBT is based on the idea that thoughts, emotions, physical sensations, behaviours and actions are all interconnected. And that by consciously changing a single component of this vicious cycle, all aspects can be improved for a better life. It is most commonly used to treat anxiety and depression, but can be useful for other mental and physical health problems as well.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1539";s:5:"count";s:2:"20";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"20";}i:32;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1470";s:4:"name";s:14:"Colour Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:14:"colour-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1470";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:362:"The different frequencies of light have a profound and healing effect on all creation. Colour Therapy aims to balance and enhance the body‚Äôs vital energy centres and chakras by using the invisible colours of the light spectrum. Colour Therapy can be used to solve any problem: physical, mental, emotional or spiritual. It is also an overall relaxation therapy.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"8";}i:33;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1559";s:4:"name";s:27:"Conscious Parent Counseling";s:4:"slug";s:29:"conscious-parenting-counselor";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1559";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:419:"Conscious Parenting Counselor sets certain beliefs in parents about what children needs to develop.The counselor helps parents to engage and connect with their children using emotionally intelligent discipline choices rather than harsh methods. The therapy supports the bond between parent and child,gives the right to the child to express his feeling, allows a child to grow as he needs to and promotes family harmony.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1557";s:5:"count";s:2:"15";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"13";}i:34;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1424";s:4:"name";s:16:"Cosmic Astrology";s:4:"slug";s:16:"cosmic-astrology";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1424";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:594:"Cosmic Astrology was established as a science in many different ancient civilizations around the world. Based on this study, the astrologer interprets the influence of stars, planets and other cosmic/ celestial objects on individual lives using the time and location of an individual‚Äôs birth, determining their zodiac sun sign, which also signifies the energy under which one‚Äôs soul chose to incarnate in this lifetime. There are numerous additional factors influencing overall karmic journey of each soul and by understanding the astrologer‚Äôs analysis, one can make an informed decision.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"9";}i:35;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1557";s:4:"name";s:10:"Counseling";s:4:"slug";s:21:"counseling-consulting";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1557";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:272:"Counseling &amp; Consulting therapies are always with trained therapists, most of whom have clinical experience, that involve a lot of talking and mind-reconditioning therapies. Deep seated emotional issues often see a marked improvement after several counseling sessions.";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:2:"22";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:36;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1477";s:4:"name";s:21:"Cranio Sacral Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:21:"cranio-sacral-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1477";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:2:"14";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"14";}i:37;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1552";s:4:"name";s:22:"Creative Visualization";s:4:"slug";s:22:"creative-visualization";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1552";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:637:"Creative Visualisation is a mental technique that uses the imagination and subtle realms of existence to make dreams and goals a reality. Used in the right way, creative visualisation can improve your life and manifest success and prosperity. It can alter your environment and circumstances by causing events to take place, attracting money, possessions, work, people and love into your life. It is a process that is similar to daydreaming, involving conscious visualisation of the reality you wish to manifest. This demonstrates the natural process and the power of intention, thought and emotion over the laws that materially manifest.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"5";}i:38;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1454";s:4:"name";s:12:"Crystal Bowl";s:4:"slug";s:12:"crystal-bowl";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1454";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:443:"Crystal Bowl Healing is normally conducted using high quality pure crystal bowls. They have been discovered to have incredibly pure sounds and are used for sound healing coupled with the intent and awareness of the healer. The rich, pure, vibrancy of tone helps the listener to relax and achieve deep states of well-being and clarity. It also helps in balancing Chakras and sometimes also induces shamanic journeys to other dimensional states.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1452";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:39;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1395";s:4:"name";s:15:"Crystal Healing";s:4:"slug";s:15:"crystal-healing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1395";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:297:"Crystal Healing or Therapy is a form of vibrational medicine that involves using the high-energy consciousness of crystals to facilitate healing. Crystals have healing vibrations that heal the receiver balancing their chakras and aura as they are a part of earth consciousness and very much alive.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"41";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"40";}i:40;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"2955";s:4:"name";s:11:"Cup Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:11:"cup-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"2955";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:511:"Cup therapy is a form of alternative therapy that traces its roots back to the ancient Chinese, Egyptian and Middle Eastern cultures.It is used to treat chronic pain- mostly back pain and headaches. It involves the placing of hot cups- made up of either silicone or plastic on the affected area. As the air inside the cup cools down, it creates a vacuum and a suction force that makes the blood vessels in that region expand, thereby improving blood circulation in the affected area and reducing muscle tension.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"4";}i:41;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1440";s:4:"name";s:13:"Dance Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:13:"dance-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1440";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:393:"Dance Therapy, also referred to as movement therapy, uses movement of the body to help individuals achieve emotional, cognitive, physical and social integration through release of emotions that could be stored within the body at a muscular and cellular level. This form of expressive therapy explores the relationship between movement and the release of emotion through various forms of dance.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1438";s:5:"count";s:2:"19";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"15";}i:42;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1510";s:4:"name";s:39:"Detoxification &amp; Energizing Devices";s:4:"slug";s:33:"detoxification-energizing-devices";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1510";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1502";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"8";}i:43;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"3776";s:4:"name";s:9:"Dietician";s:4:"slug";s:9:"dietician";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"3776";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:427:"Eating right is the key to good health. Be it for weight loss or health needs, maintaining a particular diet is essential. That‚Äôs where dieticians come in. Dieticians are experts in dietetics, that is, human nutrition. A dietician helps alter one‚Äôs diet and eating patterns based on the person‚Äôs health needs. They can diagnose nutritional problems and accordingly create meal plans and provide nutritional counseling. 
";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1557";s:5:"count";s:2:"43";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"42";}i:44;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1400";s:4:"name";s:14:"DNA Activation";s:4:"slug";s:14:"dna-activation";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1400";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:528:"DNA Activation is the awakening of human consciousness that is expressed within the unlocking of the human DNA to its hidden full potential. There are still many undiscovered mysteries within each human being. In this new consciousness, the planet has shifted into awakening and there are many who are making this shift through a re-connection with their I Am presence. One can work with the DNA and give instructions to it so that each strand can be fully activated, and the person can embrace their full potential as creators.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"11";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"10";}i:45;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1553";s:4:"name";s:23:"Dolphin Healing Network";s:4:"slug";s:23:"dolphin-healing-network";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1553";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:521:"Dolphins can help one receive powerful healing energies due to the high frequency of their own collective consciousness. It is believed that dolphins have incarnated on Earth to help heal the energy of the planet and humans. One doesn‚Äôt have to swim with dolphins to receive these healing energies; in fact practitioners who can connect with dolphins can send the energy of dolphins either in person or through a distant healing session. It can be useful to overcome physical, emotional, mental or spiritual challenges.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:46;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1433";s:4:"name";s:7:"Dowsing";s:4:"slug";s:7:"dowsing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1433";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:284:"To dowse is to search with the aid of simple hand-held tools or instruments that which is otherwise hidden from view or knowledge. It could be used to search for artifacts and entities, too. Dowsing is most commonly known by people in association with searching for underground water.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:1:"7";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"7";}i:47;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1426";s:4:"name";s:14:"Dream Analysis";s:4:"slug";s:14:"dream-analysis";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1426";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:394:"Dream Analysis is a method of gaining a deeper understanding of oneself and one‚Äôs path in life through an analysis of the symbolism, which is the subconscious material that rises to the conscious mind while we are asleep. Dreams also connect us to the subtler realms of existence and indicate messages from guides, masters or Higher Self or simply give us signs and help uncover our emotions.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:2:"11";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"7";}i:48;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1479";s:4:"name";s:33:"EFT - Emotional Freedom Technique";s:4:"slug";s:31:"eft-emotional-freedom-technique";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1479";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:293:"EFT ‚Äì Emotional Freedom Technique originated from the ancient Chinese study of Chi and the paths of energy flow. It helps to transform physical or emotional issues by tapping on the meridian points with fingertips along with a specific affirmation. It relaxes the mind and balances the body.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:2:"25";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"23";}i:49;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1527";s:4:"name";s:34:"Energetic Analysis and Corrections";s:4:"slug";s:34:"energetic-analysis-and-corrections";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1527";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1502";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:50;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1391";s:4:"name";s:14:"Energy Healing";s:4:"slug";s:14:"energy-healing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1391";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:314:"The human body holds energy centers which can lead to dis-ease when imbalanced. Energy Healing is a method of channeling healing energy into those centers to restore balance. There are many therapies that use Energy Healing, and can be hands-on, hands-off and distant (where the patient is in a different location)";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"6";}i:51;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1428";s:4:"name";s:24:"Enneagram of personality";s:4:"slug";s:24:"enneagram-of-personality";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1428";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:484:"Enneagram of Personality is a model of human personality where there are nine interconnected personality types. An Enneagram is a powerful way to understand oneself and the world deeply. Though it is common to find a little bit of oneself in every personality type, the Enneagram lets one choose the one closest to one‚Äôs basic personality type. This helps to understand, at each level, the psychological shift that occurs, thereby showing up the personality traits more objectively.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"2";}i:52;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"3581";s:4:"name";s:23:"Expressive Arts Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:22:"expressive-art-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"3581";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:628:"We all have our own ways of expressing ourselves and that is our natural way of letting our emotions flow. However, with time, we are conditioned to contain this free flow of expression and that leads to emotional imbalance. Expressive Arts therapy is an amalgamation of various art forms such as dance, music and theatre combined into experiential workshops to help you indulge in free expression and leads you to self-awareness.  It can help you rekindle your desire to create and innovate and release all the negativity that is bottled up. As a result, you start opening up to your own self and knowing your instincts better.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1438";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:53;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1550";s:4:"name";s:20:"Family Constellation";s:4:"slug";s:20:"family-constellation";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1550";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:486:"Family Constellation (Trans-generational Healing) is a dynamic therapy to heal an individual from deep underlying family patterns and trauma within their family system. This process involves taking the individual‚Äôs issues into a group with the therapist, where others in the group play roles of his/her family members. This process taps into the underlying energy dynamics of the family constellation, thereby opening up new possibilities and improving the relationships dramatically.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"26";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"25";}i:54;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1404";s:4:"name";s:9:"Feng Shui";s:4:"slug";s:9:"feng-shui";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1404";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:393:"Feng Shui is an ancient Chinese study of the flow of Chi energy. It examines how the arrangement and placement of objects within a space affects the energy flow in the environment and how these objects interact with and also influence the flow of one‚Äôs personal energy. This influences how one thinks and behaves which in turn influences every area of one‚Äôs personal and professional life.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"11";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"7";}i:55;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1512";s:4:"name";s:11:"Foot De-tox";s:4:"slug";s:11:"foot-de-tox";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1512";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:261:"Unconsciously, we acquire many toxins into our physical body via the pollution in our environment, electromagnetic radiation, food &amp; water, on a daily basis. Foot Detox aids in detoxification by throwing away the chemical toxins accumulated inside the body.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1510";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:56;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1471";s:4:"name";s:11:"Gem Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:11:"gem-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1471";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:424:"The power of therapeutic gemstones and crystals have been used in Ayurveda, Chinese medicine and Native American Shamanism. Believing that even gems have consciousness, the therapy explores the vast therapeutic possibilities that arise when gemstones are cut into spheres and their energy is systematically applied in specific protocols. This process is a new way to view the entire human organism and the nature of illness.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:57;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1547";s:4:"name";s:15:"Gestalt Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:15:"gestalt-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1547";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:460:"The German word ‚Äògestalt‚Äô means shape or form, referencing the essence of something. Gestalt therapists use experiential techniques to enhance freedom, awareness, and self-direction for the clients. This focuses more on the process than on the content as to what is discussed. Even though it is a person-centered therapy, it emphasises more on the therapist‚Äôs use of understanding, empathy and unconditional acceptance of who is sitting in front of them.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"2";}i:58;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1427";s:4:"name";s:13:"Graphotherapy";s:4:"slug";s:13:"graphotherapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1427";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:500:"Graphotherapy is a means of making conscious alterations in one‚Äôs handwriting in order to effect desired subconscious changes in the personality. This is a reversal of the normal writing process, where the hand sends messages to the brain.It seeks to address the root of various ills such as lack of persistence and determination; absence of concentration, frustration and waywardness in material life, including sex; depression; low self-esteem and inability to get over past affairs and failures.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:2:"17";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"17";}i:59;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1794";s:4:"name";s:16:"Harmonic Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:16:"harmonic-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1794";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:461:"Harmonic Life Therapy is a 3-level system of wellness. The 3 levels are MPowerment, MPowering and MPowered. At each level, a combination of modalities such as DNA Activation, Chakra healing, Aura Reading, Divine Healing Cards, Karmic Resonance, Spiritual Anatomy, Angels &amp; Crystal Therapy and Mercaba Activation are used for healing. Founded by Dr. Monica Nagpal, Harmonic Life Therapy offers solutions for a wide range of emotional and mental issues.  

";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"2";}i:60;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1411";s:4:"name";s:10:"Hatha Yoga";s:4:"slug";s:10:"hatha-yoga";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1411";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:416:"Hatha Yoga is the authentic form of yoga uncorrupted by modern practices which includes the practice of asana and pranayama, to balance the energies of the individual. This practice is meditative and slow, where one must hold the pose/asana for maximum benefits like flexibility, strength and vitality. The regular practice creates a deep sense of body awareness, feeling of serenity, calm and stillness of the mind.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1410";s:5:"count";s:3:"174";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:3:"148";}i:61;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1546";s:4:"name";s:36:"Heal your life Program by Louise Hay";s:4:"slug";s:36:"heal-your-life-program-by-louise-hay";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1546";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:821:"Heal Your Life Program by Louise Hay is based on the principles of the book You Can Heal Your Life¬Æ by Louise L. Hay. This program is about YOU, the way you are, the key influences and events in your life that have brought you to where you are now and the way you would like your life to be. The process of healing your life begins with breaking through the layers of old conditioning and beliefs about how you ‚Äúshould‚Äù lead your life, identifying the problem areas and clearing out emotional clutter connected with them. These programs provide a series of practical steps to make these changes. Some of the benefits of this program are learning to love yourself and others more fully, releasing negative emotions that block your joy and creativity, and working with the body, mind and spirit to transform your life.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"14";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"13";}i:62;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1556";s:4:"name";s:12:"Ho'oponopono";s:4:"slug";s:11:"hooponopono";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1556";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:202:"Ho‚Äôoponopono is a Hawaiian practice of reconciliation and forgiveness based on the principle that things that happen to you or in the world around you are your responsibility. It‚Äôs a 4-step process:";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:63;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1401";s:4:"name";s:19:"Holographic Healing";s:4:"slug";s:19:"holographic-healing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1401";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:536:"Holographic Healing of ancestral DNA is vibrational healing at the cutting edge. The techniques take you to your deepest self, where your ancestral stories are stored. As you discover the beliefs and feelings of your past, you will have the key to the present and clearly see the driving force behind your thoughts and emotions creating your life today. These techniques enable you with tools to assist you in the holographic repair and replacement of many genes like those for depression, fear, obesity, aging, anger, phobia and so on.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"2";}i:64;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1460";s:4:"name";s:10:"Homeopathy";s:4:"slug";s:10:"homeopathy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1460";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:574:"Homeopathy is a gentle and effective medicinal science that was developed in Germany. It does not treat superficially at the symptomatic level but heals the patient at the root level. The medicine is in the form of sugar pills that are infused with dilutions that contain the essence of natural substances treated with specific amount of vibration. It is scientific and works on the principles of quantum physics. This safe, quick and extremely effective method of healing offers long lasting to permanent cure, treating the disease from its roots, for most of the ailments.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1457";s:5:"count";s:2:"74";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"69";}i:65;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1447";s:4:"name";s:13:"Hypno Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:12:"hypnotherapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1447";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:360:"The mind, when taken to a hypnotic state through deep but conscious relaxation, can be guided to overcome past trauma, addictions, health conditions and self-limiting behaviours. It helps peel away the layers where our deepest blocks and memories are sub-consciously buried. There are many forms of hypnotherapy, all proved to be effective on different levels.";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:2:"11";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"8";}i:66;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1449";s:4:"name";s:13:"Hypnobirthing";s:4:"slug";s:13:"hypnobirthing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1449";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:432:"Hypnobirthing is a unique antenatal program that teaches simple but specific self-hypnosis and relaxation techniques for an easier, more gentle birth that is often accompanied by a significant reduction in pain. It is not about ‚Äútraining mothers to give birth‚Äù but about getting rid of the fear and allowing their bodies and minds to relax so they can birth their babies gently. It has been quoted as ‚Äòinstinctive birthing‚Äô.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1447";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:67;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1778";s:4:"name";s:12:"Hypnotherapy";s:4:"slug";s:13:"hypno-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1778";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:733:"Hypnotherapy: uses guided relaxation, concentration and focused attention to achieve a heightened state of awareness that occurs at a level of deep relaxation. In this state of mind, a person can access memories not available at the conscious level, heal aspects of the self that are wounded and the mind becomes susceptible to suggestion they can focus on specific thoughts or tasks. Hypnosis is usually considered an aid to psychotherapy (counseling or therapy) because the hypnotic state allows people to explore painful thoughts, feelings, and memories they might have hidden from their conscious minds. In addition, hypnosis enables people to perceive prior experience from a new perspective enabling immense growth and healing.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1447";s:5:"count";s:2:"78";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"77";}i:68;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1514";s:4:"name";s:9:"I - float";s:4:"slug";s:7:"i-float";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1514";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:417:"I ‚Äì Float relaxes the muscles and releases tension by allowing the user to experience a zero-gravity state. The healing takes place at a deep level of relaxation and involves the subtle aligning of the spine and de-stressing of the back muscles. The intelligent use of light and sound offers the patient deep tissue healing, and a meditative experience by helping them experience alpha &amp; theta brainwave states.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1510";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:69;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1548";s:4:"name";s:19:"Inner Child Healing";s:4:"slug";s:19:"inner-child-healing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1548";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:593:"Inner Child Work offers a thorough understanding and healing of the child within oneself and opens the floodgates to the bounty of inner being. If there was an overt abuse or neglect in one‚Äôs childhood or more subtle pressures and expectations, their psyche continues to bear childhood wounds. Everything one has ever experienced is stored in the body and mind. Events from childhood remain unhealed in most and become major contributors to the conflicts and problems experienced as adults. Inner child work shows how to give one‚Äôs Inner Child the nurturing attention it has always needed.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"46";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"44";}i:70;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"3623";s:4:"name";s:26:"Iridology &amp; Sclerology";s:4:"slug";s:20:"iridology-sclerology";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"3623";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:1087:"Both iridology and sclerology are sciences based on determining a person‚Äôs health condition by studying different parts of the eye. 
 
Iridology is a technique wherein a person‚Äôs iris color, pattern and other features are considered to be indicators of his or her systemic health. Iridology practitioners refer to something called the iris chart, where the iris is divided into many sections, each representing a part of the body. Through these charts, they can determine which organs and systems of the body are healthy and which ones are inflamed, distressed or overactive. In accordance with this information, they derive the person‚Äôs past medical problems, predict future problems and understand if the body is susceptible to certain diseases.  

In case of sclerology, the vascular patterns and whites in the sclera (the white portion of the eye) are studied to determine the overall health. 

If there is a marking in your sclera for a particular body part, it is also there in the iris in the same area. Hence, sclerology and iridology are complementary techniques. 
";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:71;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1414";s:4:"name";s:12:"Iyengar Yoga";s:4:"slug";s:12:"iyengar-yoga";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1414";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:419:"Iyengar Yoga is a form of Hatha Yoga masterminded by the great Yogi, B.K.S Iyengar. He made the secrets of the Yoga sutras by Patanjali accessible to the common man. B.K.S. Iyengar greatly emphasized in his teaching the union of body, mind and emotions through regular practice. He designed and developed the use of props such as wooden gadgets, belts and ropes to help the practitioner achieve perfection in any asana.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1410";s:5:"count";s:2:"31";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"17";}i:72;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1850";s:4:"name";s:11:"Jin Shin Do";s:4:"slug";s:9:"jinsin-do";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1850";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:827:"Jin Shin Do which means "The Way of the Compassionate Spirit" is a therapeutic acupressure technique developed by psychotherapist Iona Marsaa Teeguarden, in early 1970. It is recognized as a major form of Asian Bodywork Therapy.

It works through the use of gentle yet deep finger pressure on specific acu-points and verbal Body Focusing techniques. The therapists are non-judgemental and do not force a release. They listen to the client‚Äôs body, allowing it to direct them to areas that need attention and to dictate the pace of the session. The therapists also recognize that the mind, body and
spirit are all connected and that physical tension may indicate emotional trauma or hidden memories. They direct the client's awareness to the muscle tension and encourage them to release it through processing their emotions.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:73;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"3431";s:4:"name";s:9:"Kids Yoga";s:4:"slug";s:9:"kids-yoga";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"3431";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:572:"Yoga has often been thought of as a practice for adults, however, more often than not, kids need it more! This is because during the growing stage, kids go through a phase of intense learning and Yoga can have a calming effect on the mind and helps maintain their physical flexibility that often erodes as we grow up. Most kids also struggle with low attention spans and Yoga can be extremely beneficial in sharpening their concentration. Kids yoga enhances self-expression, boosts self-confidence and since it‚Äôs usually a group activity, it forges collaborative effort.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1410";s:5:"count";s:2:"12";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"12";}i:74;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1418";s:4:"name";s:10:"Kriya Yoga";s:4:"slug";s:10:"kriya-yoga";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1418";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:347:"Kriya Yoga is an ancient yogic practice that enables the practitioners to gain control of their inner energy by regularly practicing kriyas. It involves practicing advanced pranayamas, mantras and mudras to accelerate spiritual development. This tradition is normally taught with an initiation into the mastery of inner energy and the outer world.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1410";s:5:"count";s:2:"21";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"12";}i:75;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1399";s:4:"name";s:20:"Kundalini Activation";s:4:"slug";s:20:"kundalini-activation";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1399";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:379:"Kundalini is the divine cosmic force which is located at the base of the spine. Once activated, it can unlock spiritual siddhis and can also help one achieve enlightenment. It can be activated by spiritual masters and clears the Chakras when it flows in channels called Nadis. It results in clarity of thoughts and improved memory apart from giving relief from physical ailments.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"11";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"9";}i:76;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1415";s:4:"name";s:14:"Kundalini Yoga";s:4:"slug";s:14:"kundalini-yoga";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1415";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:443:"Kundalini Yoga is a practice originating from the school of Tantra which involves energizing and awakening the dormant cosmic life force, the Kundalini. This energy is awakened by a regular and steady practice of specific asanas, pranayama, meditation and chanting mantras. Kundalini Yoga is only meant for serious seekers who have already undergone some purification in order to be able to contain and hold the energy of the rising Kundalini.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1410";s:5:"count";s:2:"13";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"7";}i:77;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"2349";s:4:"name";s:9:"Lama Fera";s:4:"slug";s:9:"lama-fera";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"2349";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:1062:"Lama Fera is a Tibetan art of healing. Practised by Lamas it involves the use of 45 symbols of Shalvik Mantra Rahasya created with the vibrations of 4,50,000 mantras are converted into 12 special symbols + advanced 9 symbols. 

The word Lama means Disciple of lord Buddha and the word Fera means round or more specifically around the body with the energy of lord Buddha. The Energy of lord Buddha is channeled through the Healer and directed towards disease or illness. 

This system of Lama Fera heals through the release of blockages of the life force in the chakras. It helps in increasing spiritual abilities, relieve pain and discomfort caused by chronic disease, removes unwanted spirits, overcome fear, anxiety, stress and helps one connect with higher self. It is considered as the fastest healing technique for physic problems,It removes pressure of thoughts and increases the vital energy of the bodies. Though this method of healing is quite different from Reiki and other types of healing therapies, it can, like them, be used in distant healing.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"14";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"14";}i:78;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1451";s:4:"name";s:18:"Life Between Lives";s:4:"slug";s:18:"life-between-lives";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1451";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:942:"Life Between Lives (or otherwise known as ‚Äúlife between life‚Äù or ‚ÄúLBL‚Äù) is the state in which your soul is in-between two lives. It is the period from after your spirit leaves your physical body in the last life to just prior to physical incarnation in this current lifetime. This is a deep hypnotherapy process designed to reconnect with one‚Äôs soul and awaken understanding of one‚Äôs immortal identity. Some of the benefits include losing the fear of physical death and gaining a complete understanding of who you really are with sum total of your past life, reception of the newly-arrived soul, ways spirits connect with and comfort the living, organization of souls and spiritual advancement in the afterlife, meaning of Hell, spirit guides and angels, selection of a new life, soulmates, purpose of life, the birth process and how one can get assistance in connecting souls with other soul teachers and guides, amongst others.,";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1447";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"8";}i:79;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1564";s:4:"name";s:13:"Life Coaching";s:4:"slug";s:10:"life-coach";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1564";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:586:"Life Coaching changes the way clients operate at a deeper level. It does not stop at just examining behaviours, habits and goals. Life Coaching facilitates the clients to delve into their deep-rooted beliefs and thought patterns. It also helps them to connect within with their supreme power (Core of Existence). This enables the clients to become aware of their resourcefulness and to be their ‚Äòauthentic self‚Äô. By doing this, the clients are empowered to adopt new behaviours and take their performance to the next level, thereby functioning from their highest state of abundance.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1557";s:5:"count";s:3:"176";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"66";}i:80;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1520";s:4:"name";s:15:"Magnetic Pulsar";s:4:"slug";s:15:"magnetic-pulsar";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1520";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:248:"Magnetic Pulser is a small device designed to treat physiological and neurological disorders, and works on muscular relaxation. Bio magnetic impulses are used to restore the body to its original state of health. It can be used anywhere on the body.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1517";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"2";}i:81;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1407";s:4:"name";s:23:"Magnified Healing Phase";s:4:"slug";s:23:"magnified-healing-phase";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1407";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:590:"Magnified Healing Phase is a holistic approach to healing the body naturally. The practitioner combines healing energy with voice and movement. It establishes a constant flow of energy from the heart to the Source, the All That Is, through all of the spiritual centers down to the diamond at the center of the Earth. The practitioner places one hand in front of the body and the other at the back of the client who is receiving the healing. The energy goes from one hand to the other through the body of the client leading to healing on the physical, emotional, mental and spiritual levels.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"6";}i:82;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1439";s:4:"name";s:7:"Mandala";s:4:"slug";s:7:"mandala";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1439";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:392:"The Mandala is a circle that represents wholeness, a decorative cosmic diagram reminding one of their relation to infinity, extending beyond and within their body and mind. The vedic texts believe that all the past impressions called ‚Äòsamskaras‚Äô are stored in the vital body as symbols. And by meditating upon mandalas, one can awaken those experiences, emotions and memories for healing.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1438";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"3";}i:83;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1851";s:4:"name";s:7:"Mandana";s:4:"slug";s:15:"mandana-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1851";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:801:"Mandanagraphy is the drawing of sacred art forms from folk art on walls, floors and courtyards. The floor Mandana is based on 'Panchmahabhuta' - five elements of universal 'Prakriti'-The Mother Nature. Mandana is derived from the Sanskrit word ‚ÄòMandan‚Äô which means 'to invent'. This art form is drawn to get the blessings of God and shows respect towards the nature, agriculture, animate beings such as animals, small creatures, birds, tree and plants and inanimate beings. This is the only such folk art of India which is based on Spirituality and is being revived by Shri Lakhi Chand Jain. It is a wordless form of art therapy that helps the individual to access one's inner core of creative energy. Mandanagraphy helps greatly in reducing stress and enhancing one's creativity and productivity.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1438";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:84;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1561";s:4:"name";s:19:"Marriage Counseling";s:4:"slug";s:18:"marriage-counselor";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1561";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:340:"Marriage Counselor helps people with relationship problems. He/she can help the couple to work through conflicts and communication gaps and discover various ways to deal with the problem that might arise in the future. A marriage counselor helps reduce the divorce rate, promotes healthy relationships and helps avoid future major problems.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1557";s:5:"count";s:2:"26";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"17";}i:85;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1487";s:4:"name";s:15:"Massage Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:15:"massage-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1487";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:442:"Massage Therapy is a manual massage of soft body tissues to enhance and relax the muscles, which in turn leads to the relaxation of the mind. A massage therapist is trained with a deep understanding of human anatomy and how sensations and touch can stimulate healing. It is used to reduce stress and anxiety, relax muscles, rehabilitate injuries, and reduce depression and chronic pain while promoting overall health and a sense of wellbeing.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1485";s:5:"count";s:2:"29";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"25";}i:86;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1785";s:4:"name";s:10:"Meditation";s:4:"slug";s:10:"meditation";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1785";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:367:"Meditation is a state of thoughtless awareness, not an action but a state of being. Meditation is a state of profound deep peace that occurs when the mind is calm and silent, yet completely alert. The regular practice of meditation can take one to higher levels of self-awareness and peace along with increased cognitive functions, lowering anxiety and stress levels.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1491";s:5:"count";s:3:"202";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"96";}i:87;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1491";s:4:"name";s:11:"Meditations";s:4:"slug";s:11:"meditations";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1491";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:537:"Meditation is now scientifically proven to significantly lower stress levels, boost immunity, and increase coherence at all levels. Typically, meditation involves focusing on the breath, an object, or a mental vision that helps lower brain waves from active high beta waves to alpha and theta brain waves. At these levels of the brain, a lot of healing and transformation can spontaneously occur. There are many different types of meditations and all of them with regular practice can train attention and awareness, and regulate emotions";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:2:"93";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"3";}i:88;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1444";s:4:"name";s:12:"Mind Mapping";s:4:"slug";s:12:"mind-mapping";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1444";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:505:"Mind Mapping is a powerful tool to help people illustrate how wounds from their childhood were delivered, stored and how they could be healed. Mind mapping can help people reach the core of their negative belief system. Once they recognize their belief systems, they can see and understand how it affects their whole life. Through mind mapping, one can see the bigger picture and transform deep-seated beliefs into positive ones. It is easy to use and can be done with couples, families, individuals, etc.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1438";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"2";}i:89;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1493";s:4:"name";s:11:"Mindfulness";s:4:"slug";s:11:"mindfulness";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1493";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:641:"Mindfulness is the art and science of finding focus and stability in one‚Äôs daily life. Mindfulness helps individuals become aware of and experience the present moment and empowers them with response-ability. Being mindful in every action or being present in every moment can help one connect with one‚Äôs true nature, which is simply ‚Äòbeing‚Äô. Most people live either in regret of the past or worry of the future but the past and future are both like dreams, so becoming mindful roots one in the present ‚ÄòNow‚Äô moment. Doing this opens up the universe of opportunities to make the most of one‚Äôs life and find meaning and happiness.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1491";s:5:"count";s:2:"28";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"13";}i:90;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1416";s:4:"name";s:6:"Mudras";s:4:"slug";s:6:"mudras";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1416";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:451:"Mudras are the subtle physiological postures adopted by the body to alter the flow of prana (cosmic energy), within the physical body.The use of mudra is a powerful key for linking the material and psychic realms. Mudras sensitize the mind to the experiences of the pranic body. The purpose of the Mudra is to evoke inner forces which otherwise lie dormant in the body and also to access spiritual realms and this is what makes Mudras a powerful tool.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1410";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:91;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1434";s:4:"name";s:12:"Nadi Shastra";s:4:"slug";s:12:"nadi-shastra";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1434";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:433:"Nadi Shastra is a form of Dharma astrology. It is based on the belief that the life of all human beings was predicted by dharma sages during ancient times which was then written on palm leaves, more than thousands of years ago. These writings include recorded facts of one‚Äôs life ‚Äì past, present and future with an explanation of how to cleanse one‚Äôs life of past sins by following the prescribed penances and preventive steps.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:92;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1473";s:4:"name";s:12:"Nadi Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:12:"nadi-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1473";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:365:"Nadi Therapy is an ancient therapy where a practitioner can reveal the past, present and future ailments along with the root cause of the individual‚Äôs ailments by merely checking the pulse. This therapy can be a preventive cure often alerting patients of major illnesses before the symptoms show up, allowing intervention and cures, from simple to chronic issues.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:93;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1472";s:4:"name";s:50:"Nambudripad's Allergy Elimination Technique (NAET)";s:4:"slug";s:42:"nambudripads-allergy-elimination-technique";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1472";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:404:"Nambudripad‚Äôs Allergy Elimination Technique (NAET) was discovered by Dr. Devi S. Nambudripad in November of 1983. It is a non-invasive, drug free, natural solution to alleviate allergies of all types and intensities using a blend of selective energy balancing, testing and treatment procedures from acupuncture/acupressure, allopathy, chiropractic, nutritional, and kinesiology disciplines of medicine.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"3";}i:94;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1458";s:4:"name";s:11:"Naturopathy";s:4:"slug";s:11:"naturopathy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1458";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:505:"When one goes against nature, one falls ill. The healing happens only when the disease (toxins) is expelled from the body. Naturopathy cures diseases without the use of any medicines. Instead, it involves earth and nature to bring a balance into one‚Äôs body, which again is composed of the 5 elements. Naturopathy empowers the human body to heal itself by working on the immune system in the fuller sense of both, the physical and the psyche, which is responsible for one‚Äôs overall health and wellness.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1457";s:5:"count";s:2:"41";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"33";}i:95;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1522";s:4:"name";s:40:"NeuroSky MindWave &amp; Mind Workstation";s:4:"slug";s:34:"neurosky-mindwave-mind-workstation";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1522";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:194:"NeuroSky Mind Wave &amp; Mind Workstation uses dry EEG sensors to measure and monitor brain wave states in real-time. It is also capable of brainwave entrainment using bio-feedback optimization.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1521";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:96;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1500";s:4:"name";s:16:"Nichren Buddhism";s:4:"slug";s:16:"nichren-buddhism";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1500";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1499";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"3";}i:97;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1543";s:4:"name";s:33:"NLP- Neuro-Linguistic Programming";s:4:"slug";s:32:"nlp-neuro-linguistic-programming";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1543";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:472:"Neuro-Linguistic Programming Therapy (NLP) describes the dynamic between neuro, which is mind, and linguistic which is language and how their conjunction affects one‚Äôs body and behavior. It aids one with anger management, stress management, anxiety, pain management and improving performance. The therapists could be effective without even knowing the problem in detail. This typically resolves issues in several brief sessions and tends to be pretty quick with results.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:2:"47";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"42";}i:98;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1551";s:4:"name";s:25:"Non-violent communication";s:4:"slug";s:25:"non-violent-communication";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1551";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:446:"Non-violent Communication (NVC) is based on the principles of nonviolence ‚Äì the natural state of compassion when no violence is present in the heart. NVC begins by believing that we are all-compassionate by nature and that violent strategies, whether verbal or physical, are learned behaviors. People who practice NVC have found greater authenticity in their communication, increased understanding, deepening connection and conflict resolution.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"3";}i:99;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1423";s:4:"name";s:10:"Numerology";s:4:"slug";s:10:"numerology";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1423";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:600:"According to Numerology, the Universe speaks in the language of numbers that it is not random but one that works through a mathematical approach. Numerologists also believe that each one of us has three numbers that are the most relevant: Psychic Number, Destiny Number and Name Number. They are well-versed in this ancient study which includes the analysis of numbers, patterns, their invisible influence, energetic relevance and their significance in our lives. Numerologists often suggest methods to alter these numbers to help us get rid of karmic blocks and throw open a flow of positive energy.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1419";s:5:"count";s:2:"53";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"49";}i:100;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1563";s:4:"name";s:12:"Nutritionist";s:4:"slug";s:12:"nutritionist";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1563";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:342:"A Nutritionist advises on food and nutrition which impacts one‚Äôs health. Well-maintained nutrition is important for healthy living and an overall well-being. A nutritionist develops meal goals, educates on portion control and provides special diets for the treatment and prevention of chronic ailments such as diabetes, heart diseases, etc.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1557";s:5:"count";s:3:"228";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:3:"145";}i:101;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1494";s:4:"name";s:23:"Osho Dynamic Meditation";s:4:"slug";s:23:"osho-dynamic-meditation";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1494";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:605:"Osho Dynamic Meditation was founded by Bhagwan Shree Rajneesh Osho, better known as just ‚ÄúOsho‚Äù. In this meditation, one has to be completely conscious, alert and continuously aware of every action. It is a specific technique that lasts for an hour, including a sequence of 5 steps: breathing, catharsis (expressing yourself in whichever way you find comfortable), chanting the mantra ‚ÄòHoo‚Äô, being still and celebrating in the form of dance. The meditation provides benefits of inner peace, silence, better attention, concentration, calming influence, stress management and freedom from addiction.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1491";s:5:"count";s:2:"31";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"4";}i:102;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1517";s:4:"name";s:15:"Pain Management";s:4:"slug";s:15:"pain-management";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1517";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:0:"";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1502";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"8";}i:103;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1463";s:4:"name";s:10:"Panchkarma";s:4:"slug";s:10:"panchkarma";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1463";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:364:"Panchkarma is a process developed by the study of Ayurveda for detoxification and purification through 5 therapies along with special detoxification diet. The combination of these therapies cleanses the body of its toxins in various ways, uses herbal medicines and oils as a method for healing and preventive therapy, which can also purify the mind, body and soul.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1457";s:5:"count";s:2:"12";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"10";}i:104;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1448";s:4:"name";s:20:"Past Life Regression";s:4:"slug";s:20:"past-life-regression";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1448";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:738:"Past Life Regression is based on the belief that we carry the memory of all of our lives and experiences deep within our psyches/causal bodies. By using hypnotherapy, the therapist helps the patient to delve deep into their psyche and access past memories from other reincarnations that still affect the individual at a subconscious level. Once this information has been received, the therapist can help the patient complete the healing, at both conscious and subconscious levels.

<strong>It can solve:</strong> Trauma,Panic Attack,Fear &amp; Beleifs in destructive dark energies ,Birth Trauma,Post Traumatic Stress Disorder,Suicidal Tendancies ,Trauma of Sudden Death,Trauma of Sexual Abuse,Phobia ,Addiction issue,Clinical Depression";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1447";s:5:"count";s:3:"103";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"85";}i:105;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1484";s:4:"name";s:13:"Physiotherapy";s:4:"slug";s:13:"physiotherapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1484";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:803:"Physiotherapy is a form of treatment that focuses on the science of movement and helps people to restore and/or maintain their physical strength, function, motion and overall well-being by addressing the underlying physical issues. Some of the techniques include Joint mobilisation (gentle gliding) techniques, Joint manipulation, Physiotherapy Instrument Mobilisation (PIM),Minimal Energy Techniques (METs), Muscle stretching, Neurodynamics, Massage and soft tissue techniques,Acupuncture and Dry Needling,Physiotherapy Taping. Benefits include preventing injury and disability; managing acute and chronic conditions, improving and maintaining optimal physical performance, rehabilitating injury and the effects of disease or disability and educating patients to prevent the re-occurrence of an injury.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1475";s:5:"count";s:2:"16";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:2:"16";}i:106;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1409";s:4:"name";s:16:"Polarity Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:16:"polarity-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1409";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:746:"Polarity Therapy is a holistic practice which was created in the late 19th century by Dr. Randolph Stone. A mixture of both Eastern and Western energy therapies, Polarity Therapy believes that an electromagnetic energy field surrounds the body and moves between its poles (positive, negative and neutral). The energy centers are based on the Ayurvedic chakras and the Traditional Chinese Medicine principle of yin and yang. Any blockage to the smooth and balanced flow of this energy causes dis-ease in the body. The Human Energy Field is affected by diet, touch, exercise, relationships and life experience. Polarity Therapy works on the principle of balancing these effects through bodywork, touch, exercises, counseling and nutritional advice.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"2";}i:107;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1405";s:4:"name";s:20:"Prana Violet Healing";s:4:"slug";s:20:"prana-violet-healing";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1405";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:551:"Prana Violet Healing is a simple Energy healing technique where healing is done using the Prana Healing Wand (a Divine Tool used to sense Energy and to Heal ‚Äì all participants will be given a Wand). You can heal yourself, heal others ans also do distant healing for anyone who may be present anywhere in this world. Healing is done following the Universal Divine Law of Karma which is also known as the Law of Action and Reaction. Prana Violet Healing helps one understand the root cause of suffering or disease and then heal it in a systematic way.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1391";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:108;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1537";s:4:"name";s:9:"Pranayama";s:4:"slug";s:9:"pranayama";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1537";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:504:"Pranayama is the ancient yogic practice of controlling the mind using breath through conscious breathing exercises. Pranayama also balances the prana in the right and left hemispheres of the body and cleanses the nadis of blocks to stimulate a smoother flow of energy. The yogis taught that the mind and breath are intimately connected; our state of mind affects our breathing and similarly breathing can help change one‚Äôs state 