ked by solid scientific evidence are able to penetrate and diagnose the energy fields of an individual, pinpoint the imbalanced energy, and generate a high vibrational field that heals all issues.";s:6:"parent";s:1:"0";s:5:"count";s:1:"7";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"1";}i:116;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1508";s:4:"name";s:42:"Quantum Resonance Magnetic Health Analyzer";s:4:"slug";s:42:"quantum-resonance-magnetic-health-analyzer";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1508";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:592:"Quantum Resonance Magnetic Health Analyser (QRMHA) tracks the optimal functioning of the body‚Äôs major systems, organs and glands based on sensing electromagnetic signals from the body. A sensor rod held in the hand of the patient collects data on various systems of the body using electrical impulses via ‚Äúskin conductance‚Äù. Health data of 23 parameters is collected within minutes from various body systems. QRMHA replaces the need for ultrasonic, nuclear magnetic resonance or radiography for various health related conditions. Mostly recommended for Primary or Preventive Healthcare.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1503";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"3";}i:117;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1541";s:4:"name";s:36:"Rational Emotive Behavioural Therapy";s:4:"slug";s:36:"rational-emotive-behavioural-therapy";s:10:"term_group";s:1:"0";s:16:"term_taxonomy_id";s:4:"1541";s:8:"taxonomy";s:7:"therapy";s:11:"description";s:347:"Rational Emotive Behavioural Therapy is an active-directive, solution-oriented therapy that is focused on resolving emotional, cognitive and behavioural problems in individuals. Rational Emotive Behavioural Therapy teaches us to identify, evaluate, dispute, and act against one‚Äôs own irrational self- defeating beliefs through the use of reason.";s:6:"parent";s:4:"1539";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:8:"COUNT(*)";s:1:"6";}i:118;O:8:"stdClass":10:{s:7:"term_id";s:4:"1419";s:4:"name";s:20:"Readings and Rituals";s:4:"